 />\n之後攞住封信 可以去公立私家睇都得<br />\n慳錢又慳時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9903a734625b7587eb974517a08b93378512cc","tid":2456693,"uid":207677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"127b773d79679369d43b6d6858b38ed6327f6c74","tid":2456693,"uid":34517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95d0dddca719f1dbcfbb4e29703e1b4f674748d9","tid":2456693,"uid":207677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff174016371e88cff703f52ca4ab03f391dd1fc0","tid":2456693,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"有情緒病就睇醫生啦 抑鬱係香港好平常啦 有自殺傾向大機會要留醫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"成日都好多藉口, 踏唔出依步, 覺得好浪費時間同錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 冇膽, 冇人陪, 同埋有識人睇左5-6年醫生都冇好轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更加唔想睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"抑鬱其中一個病徵就係冇動力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你踏唔出都正常<br />\n不過唔好覺得一定會浪費金錢時間 <br />\n就算冇好轉 其實都代表冇惡化 最少叫控制到病情<br />\n<br />\nbtw 睇醫生好得返都大有人在 e.g.張繼聰夫婦<br />\n冇錢咪睇公立啦<br />\n冇人陪就自己睇啦 仲可以少個人知冇咁煩添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知你返工定返學 <br />\n搵一日咁啱想射波唔返既 <br />\n橫掂都去開睇醫生攞假紙<br />\n可以順便話埋俾佢聽想自殺 <br />\n叫佢寫封轉介信俾你睇精神科 <br />\n之後攞住封信 可以去公立私家睇都得<br />\n慳錢又慳時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學生+返工, 每日都好攰, 一諗到要成日覆診,就卻步<img src=\"/assets/faces/no